===Models=== *[[ASUS RT-AC66U B1]] (V2) BCM4709A0 (@1.0GHz) *[[ASUS RT-AC67U]] (R/W) *[[ASUS RT-AC1750]] (R/W/V2) *[[ASUS RT-AC1900]] (R/V2) BCM4709A0 (@1.0GHz) *[[ASUS RT-AC1900P]] BCM4709C0 (@1.4GHz)
===Overview=== *Powerful 1.4GHz dual-core processor for fast and responsive :performance with Wi-Fi, Ethernet and USB devices *Concurrent dual-band data rates of 1900Mbps for three times :faster performance than 802.11n routers *Broadcom TurboQAM technology increases wireless-N data rate :to 600Mbps for 33% faster performance *3x Smart high-performance dual band Wi-Fi detachable 5dBi antenna *5x Gigabit Ethernet ports for fast, stable wired network connections *2x USB ports with USB 3.0 for faster data transfer than USB 2.0 *ASUS AiCloud cloud service to access, sync, share, and stream :your data wherever you are, even connect to other compatible :routers creating a private cloud server with family and friends *This model is sold exclusively at Best Buy
===Features=== *Airtime Fairness, Adaptive QoS, AiProtection, Parental Control *Dual WAN, IPTV support, Roaming Assist, Guest Network (3x) *VPN server: IPSec Pass-Through, PPTP Pass-Through, :L2TP Pass-Through, PPTP Server, OpenVPN Server *VPN client: PPTP client, L2TP client, OpenVPN client *Mac OS Backup, Enhanced media server (AiPlayer App comp.) :Image: jpeg, Audio: mp3, wma, wav, pcm, mp4, lpcm, ogg :Video: asf, avi, divx, mpeg, mpg, ts, vob, wmv, mkv, mov *AiCloud personal cloud service, 3G/4G data sharing *Printer Server: LPR protocol support :Multifunctional printer support (Windows only) *Download Master: Download scheduling :Support bt, nzb, http, ed2k :Support encryption, DHT, PEX and magnet link :Upload and download bandwidth control *AiDisk file server: :Samba and FTP server with account management
